725812f-a.title: Queens: 115th Street - 10th Avenue
725812f-a.text:
115th Street, east side, just south of 10th Avenue, showing the A. D. Schlesinger house on the 2.25 acre estate. It appears in Beers's 1873 atlas of Long Island. 115th Street was previously
called West Boulevard.
P. L. Sperr  March 12, 1932
